00:13:27,560 --> 00:13:29,960
You dare hit me?

283
00:13:31,480 --> 00:13:32,960
Can't take it already?

284
00:13:33,800 --> 00:13:34,800
Ti Cha.

285
00:13:35,360 --> 00:13:36,600
Let me see.

286
00:13:36,840 --> 00:13:38,440
Who's better, you or Huo Xiao?

287
00:13:43,680 --> 00:13:44,680
That hurts already?

288
00:13:45,360 --> 00:13:47,000
Guess you're still not up to it.

289
00:13:47,600 --> 00:13:49,536
Young Master, Young Master.

290
00:13:49,560 --> 00:13:50,680
Miss Fang Yao is back.

291
00:13:50,920 --> 00:13:52,240
She dares to come back?

292
00:13:53,240 --> 00:13:54,240
Tell the Steward

293
00:13:54,320 --> 00:13:55,440
to make her get lost.

294
00:13:58,360 --> 00:13:59,816
Tell her to get lost.

295
00:13:59,840 --> 00:14:00,896
Tell her to get lost!

296
00:14:00,920 --> 00:14:01,720
But...

297
00:14:01,920 --> 00:14:03,096
Miss Fang Yao said

298
00:14:03,120 --> 00:14:04,520
she's pregnant with your child.

299
00:14:26,750 --> 00:14:29,890
♪ Mist coils around the sleeping forest ♪

300
00:14:30,360 --> 00:14:33,540
♪ Memories scattered
through cracks of darkness ♪

301
00:14:33,920 --> 00:14:37,390
♪ How to escape this real-feeling dream ♪

302
00:14:40,940 --> 00:14:44,190
♪ Lies reflect in water's gleam ♪

303
00:14:44,420 --> 00:14:47,760
♪ Traces of existence
can never be erased ♪

304
00:14:48,040 --> 00:14:51,320
♪ How to find the self I can't reclaim ♪

305
00:14:53,640 --> 00:15:00,710
♪ Fly away, hear she says ♪

306
00:15:00,790 --> 00:15:04,736
♪ She'll fly out from
thorns of woven lies ♪

307
00:15:04,760 --> 00:15:08,346
♪ Pierce the fog,
shatter this dream tonight ♪

308
00:15:08,370 --> 00:15:11,300
♪ Burn like fire ♪

309
00:15:11,330 --> 00:15:14,740
♪ Just burn like fire ♪

310
00:15:14,950 --> 00:15:18,840
♪ The maze in the abyss starts to clear ♪

311
00:15:18,880 --> 00:15:21,566
♪ Yet night keep on whispering ♪

312
00:15:21,590 --> 00:15:24,730
♪ Surrender to fate,
no clear direction ahead ♪

313
00:15:25,010 --> 00:15:28,510
♪ She will rise as the dawn
that breaks the darkness ♪

314
00:15:28,590 --> 00:15:35,050
♪ Never slowing down,
for tomorrow cannot be stopped ♪

315
00:15:35,700 --> 00:15:39,016
♪ Surrender to love and find the way ♪

316
00:15:39,040 --> 00:15:42,570
♪ Even if fate tries to forget her ♪

317
00:15:42,790 --> 00:15:49,320
♪ Never despair,
for the heart burns with endless light ♪

318
00:15:49,720 --> 00:15:51,580
♪ Waiting for dawn ♪

